# TQ-4: Test Quality Rule
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: New test creation

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Test Quality: Meaningful, maintainable, and correct test cases.

ENFORCE: All tests must be meaningful, maintainable, and intention-revealing.
PROHIBIT: Poorly written, confusing, redundant, or implementation-coupled tests.
ON VIOLATION: Halt skill execution → notify orchestrator and responsible QA Skill.
